{"tid":2335452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那麥當勞推出午餐肉+曲奇碎漢堡包","createTime":"2020-12-22T02:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T21:24:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"c54da1df0e6f39e7b1cd941e64040fa0ce4cc8ad","tid":2335452,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"BEIJING (AP) &mdash; McDonald&rsquo;s is selling a sandwich made of Spam topped with crushed Oreo cookies Monday in China in an attention-grabbing move that has raised eyebrows.<br />\nGlobal brands from restaurants to automakers sometimes roll out offbeat products to appeal to Chinese tastes in the populous and intensely competitive market.<br />\nThis is undoubtedly one of them.<br />\n&ldquo;I thought it was delicious,&rdquo; said a comment signed Feifei Mao Enthusiast on the Sina Weibo microblog service. &ldquo;Is that because I love McDonald&rsquo;s too deeply? Or is something wrong with my taste?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe sandwich is made of two slices of Spam, a product of Hormel Foods LLC, and Mondelez International&rsquo;s Oreo cookies, topped with mayonnaise.<br />\nMcDonald&rsquo;s Corp. said the sandwich was part of a series of &ldquo;members only&rdquo; promotions to be released on Mondays in China.<br />\n&ldquo;There is no need to release unnecessary products,&rdquo; said a comment left on the company&rsquo;s microblog account. It received more than 2,000 &ldquo;likes.&rdquo;<br />\nMcDonald&rsquo;s said it planned to sell no more than 400,000 of the &ldquo;Lunchmeat Burgers.&rdquo; It wasn&rsquo;t clear how many have been sold or how many people who flooded social media with scathing comments had eaten one.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;When you hate someone but have to invite him to dinner, you can ask him to eat McDonald&rsquo;s Oreo lunchmeat burger,&rdquo; said a separate comment on Sina Weibo.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/2020/12/21/mcdonalds-sells-spam-burger-with-cookie-crumbs-china/?fbclid=IwAR3rM-vM2fw6wSG8dp8U4JETXjU2m5pQkBBvOAPTbDjPJx9rof9Scl4wwzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawaiinewsnow.com%2F2020%2F12%2F21%2Fmcdonalds-sells-spam-burger-with-cookie-crumbs-china%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3rM-vM2fw6wSG8dp8U4JETXjU2m5pQkBBvOAPTbDjPJx9rof9Scl4wwzk&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=39c6e5ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/2020/12/21/mcdonalds-sells-spam-burger-with-cookie-crumbs-china/?fbclid=IwAR3rM-vM2fw6wSG8dp8U4JETXjU2m5pQkBBvOAPTbDjPJx9rof9Scl4wwzk</a>"},{"pid":"544eebd6d020931f6c98e7ec398710e80481bfca","tid":2335452,"uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":207,"score":-204,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWMG4g1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWMG4g1.jpg&h=899587a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfaa80e5964fc68d468581472c93fc90e76a6b54","tid":2335452,"uid":92435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42431a135f4483126dce091abad2c2a2ad8762fb","tid":2335452,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452fc80804e39cf32b0cbc276e978c1bec84a379","tid":2335452,"uid":155095,"like":64,"dislike":3,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/12/08ls4p2a.jpg/revision/latest/top-crop/width/450/height/450?cb=20090718034455\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F12%2F08ls4p2